body: @lukeisontheroad We're still moving around stuff internally; it's ending up being a bit tricky to open-source. In the meantime there is the [TF YOLO detector](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/tensorflow/examples/android/src/org/tensorflow/demo/TensorFlowYoloDetector.java) which you should be able to find training walkthroughs for online.
